        </p>
      </center>
      <br>

      <strong id='info-header'> Features designed by us. Requested by you. </strong>
      <center>

        <br>
        <div style='width: 575px;'>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Search, sort, and track employee certifications.
                           Email notifications for expirations.'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              Certification <br/> Tracking
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Coming Soon!'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              Chemical <br/> Records <br/>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Manage employee contact & HR info,
                           certifications, position, location, and more.'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              Employee <br/> Management
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div style='width: 575px;'>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Submit pending maintenance
                           requests. Email notifications for supervisors.'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              Maintenance <br/> Help Desk
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Coming soon!'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
             Scheduling
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Quick and easy shift reporting for employees. Know
                           more as a supervisor.'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              Shift <br/> Reports <br/>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style='width: 575px;'>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Mobile friendly checklist of mandated slide
                           inspection items.'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              Slide <br/> Inspections
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Coming Soon!'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              Private Lessons <br/> Management <br/>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='square pull-left'
               data-hover='Coming Soon!'>
            <div class='position-square-text'>
              To-Do List
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

